"><p>自由度为3</p><p>刚体的平动, 两个杆与竖直方向的夹角</p>
</div>" style="pluginMarkdown=1;text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1"> <mxGeometry x="270" y="690" width="220" height="90" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="JKrzoW_Ts3fGAIjPj_ez-2" value="" style="endArrow=none;html=1;rounded=0;strokeWidth=3;" edge="1" parent="1"> <mxGeometry width="50" height="50" relative="1" as="geometry"> <mxPoint x="60" y="780" as="sourcePoint" /> <mxPoint x="720" y="780" as="targetPoint" /> </mxGeometry> </mxCell> <mxCell id="JKrzoW_Ts3fGAIjPj_ez-3" value="<div data-content="由 Hamilton 原理

$$\int \delta T + \delta W d t = 0$$

由$\delta W = - \delta V + \delta W_{nc}$

$$\int \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc}d t = 0$$

记坐标原点为$P$

$$
\begin{cases}
PO &amp;= (x, 0) \\
OA &amp;= (L \sin \theta_1,L \cos \theta_1) \\
AB &amp;= (L \sin \theta_2,L \cos \theta_2) \\
PO1&amp;= PO + \frac{1}{2}OA \\
PA &amp;= PO + OA \\
PO2&amp;= PA + \frac{1}{2}AB \\
PB &amp;= PA + AB
\end{cases}
$$

则能量

$$
\begin{cases}
E_M &amp;= \frac{1}{2}M \dot {PO}^2 \\
E_{m_1} &amp;= \frac{1}{2}m \dot {PO_1}^2 + \frac{1}{2}J \dot \theta_1 ^2\\
E_{m_2} &amp;= \frac{1}{2}m \dot {PO_2}^2 + \frac{1}{2}J \dot \theta_2 ^2\\
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
T &amp;= E_M + E_{m_1} + E_{m_2} \\
&amp;=\frac{1}{2} M \dot{x}^2 + \frac{1}{2} m \left( \frac{1}{4} L^2 \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin^2 \theta_1 + \left( \frac{1}{2} L \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \dot{x} \right)^2 \right) + \frac{1}{2} J \dot{\theta}_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} m \left( \left( -L \dot{\theta}_1 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L \dot{\theta}_2 \sin \theta_2 \right)^2 + \left( L \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + \dot{x} \right)^2 \right) + \frac{1}{2} J \dot{\theta}_2^2 \\
&amp;= {\frac{1}{2}J\dot \theta _1^2 + \frac{5}{8}{L^2}m\dot \theta _1^2 + \frac{1}{2}J\dot \theta _2^2 + \frac{1}{8}{L^2}m\dot \theta _2^2 + m{{\dot x}^2} + \frac{1}{2}M{{\dot x}^2} + \frac{3}{2}Lm{{\dot \theta }_1}\dot x\cos {\theta _1} + \frac{1}{2}{L^2}m{{\dot \theta }_1}{{\dot \theta }_2}\cos ({\theta _1} - {\theta _2}) + \frac{1}{2}Lm{{\dot \theta }_2}\dot x\cos {\theta _2}}
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta T &amp;= \frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{x}} \delta \dot{x} + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} \delta \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} \delta \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial x} \delta x + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_1} \delta \theta_1 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_2} \delta \theta_2
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{x}} &amp;= 2 m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} &amp;= J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} &amp;= J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial x} &amp;= 0 \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_1} &amp;= -\frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{x} \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_2} &amp;= \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \dot{x} \sin \theta_2
\end{cases}
$$

势能

$$
\begin{cases}
E_{k_1} &amp;= \frac{1}{2} k_1 x^2 \\
E_{k_2} &amp;= \frac{1}{2} k_2 x^2 \\
E_{k_T} &amp;= \frac{1}{2} k_T \theta_1^2 \\
E_{g_1} &amp;= m g \left(L-\frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_1\right) \\
E_{g_2} &amp;= m g \left(2L - L \cos \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_2\right) \\
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
V &amp;= E_{k_1} + E_{k_2} + E_{k_T} + E_{g_1} + E_{g_2} \\
&amp;=\frac{1}{2} k_1 x^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 x^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_t \theta_1^2 + mg\left(L - \frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_1\right) + mg\left(2L - L \cos \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_2\right)
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\frac{\partial V}{\partial x} = k_1 x + k_2 x \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{x}} = 0 \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \theta_1} = k_t \theta_1 + \frac{3 L mg \sin \theta_1}{2} \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} = 0 \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \theta_2} = \frac{L mg \sin \theta_2}{2} \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} = 0
\end{cases}
$$

非保守力做功

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W_{nc} &amp;= -F \delta PB_x \\
&amp;= -F \delta(L \sin \theta_1 + L \sin \theta_2 + x
)\\
&amp;= -F L \cos \theta_1 \delta \theta_1 - F L \cos \theta_2 \delta \theta_2 - F \delta x
\end{align*}
$$

分别考虑三项

考虑$x$

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} \, dt &amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} (\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{x}} \delta \dot{x} + \frac{\partial T}{\partial {x}} \delta {x}) - (\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{x}} \delta \dot{x} + \frac{\partial V}{\partial {x}} \delta {x}) + (- F \delta x) \, dt\\
&amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left [\left( 2m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \dot{x} - (k_1 + k_2)x \delta x - F \delta x \right ]d t \\
&amp;= \left( 2m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta x \bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} \\
&amp;\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \frac{d}{dt} \left( 2m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta x \, dt \\
&amp;\quad- \int_{t_1}^{t_2}((k_1 + k_2)x + F) \delta x \, dt \\
&amp;= -\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( 2m \ddot{x} + M \ddot{x} - \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2^2 \sin \theta_2 + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F \right) \delta x \, dt
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\delta x$的任意性, 所以

$$2m \ddot{x} + M \ddot{x} - \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2^2 \sin \theta_2 + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F = 0$$

考虑$\theta_1$

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} \, dt
&amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} (\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} \delta \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial {\theta}_1} \delta {\theta}_1) - (\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} \delta \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{\partial V}{\partial {\theta}_1} \delta {\theta}_1) + (- F L \cos \theta_1 \delta \theta_1) \, dt\\
&amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left [\left( J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \dot{\theta}_1 \right. \\
&amp;\quad + \left( -\frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{x} \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \theta_1 \\
&amp;\quad \left. - \left( k_t \theta_1 + \frac{3 L mg \sin \theta_1}{2}\right) \delta \theta_1 - F L \cos \theta_1 \delta \theta_1 \right ]d t \\
&amp;= \left( J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \theta_1 \bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} \\
&amp;\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \frac{d}{dt} \left( J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \theta_1 \, dt \\
&amp;\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{x} \sin \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + k_t \theta_1 + \frac{3 L mg \sin \theta_1}{2} + F L \cos \theta_1 \right) \delta \theta_1 \, dt \\
&amp;= -\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( F L \cos(\theta_1) + \theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_2^2}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1) \ddot{x}}{2} \right) \delta \theta_1 \, dt
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\delta \theta_1$的任意性, 所以

$$F L \cos(\theta_1) + \theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_2^2}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1) \ddot{x}}{2} =0$$

考虑$\theta_2$

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} \, dt
&amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} (\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} \delta \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial {\theta}_2} \delta {\theta}_2) - (\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} \delta \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{\partial V}{\partial {\theta}_2} \delta {\theta}_2) + (- F L \cos \theta_2 \delta \theta_2) \, dt \\
&amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left [\left( J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \dot{\theta}_2 \right. \\
&amp;\quad + \left( \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \dot{x} \sin \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \\
&amp;\quad \left. - \left( \frac{L mg \sin \theta_2}{2} \right) \delta \theta_2 - F L \cos \theta_2 \delta \theta_2 \right ]d t \\
&amp;= \left( J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} \\
&amp;\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \frac{d}{dt} \left( J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \, dt \\
&amp;\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( -\frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \dot{x} \sin \theta_2 + \frac{L mg \sin \theta_2}{2} + F L \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \, dt \\
&amp;= F L \cos(\theta_2) + \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} - \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_1^2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \cos(\theta_2) \ddot{x}}{2}
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\delta \theta_2$的任意性, 所以

$$F L \cos(\theta_2) + \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} - \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_1^2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \cos(\theta_2) \ddot{x}}{2} = 0$$

综上, EOM 为

$$
\begin{cases}
2m \ddot{x} + M \ddot{x} - \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2^2 \sin \theta_2 + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F &amp;= 0 \\
F L \cos(\theta_1) + \theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_2^2}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1) \ddot{x}}{2} &amp;=0 \\
F L \cos(\theta_2) + \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} - \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_1^2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \cos(\theta_2) \ddot{x}}{2} &amp;= 0
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
(k_1 + k_2)x = 0 \\
\theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} = 0 \\
\frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} = 0
\end{cases}
\Rightarrow 
\begin{cases}
x &amp;= 0 \\
\theta_1 &amp;= 0 \\
\theta_2 &amp;= 0
\end{cases}
$$

线性化, 忽略高阶无穷小

$$
\begin{align}
\sin \theta = \theta \\
\cos \theta = 1 \\
y^2 = 0
\end{align}
$$

则有

$$
\begin{cases}
(2m + M) \ddot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F = 0 \\
\theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \theta_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \ddot{x}}{2} + F L = 0 \\
\frac{g L m \theta_2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \ddot{x}}{2} + F L = 0
\end{cases}
$$

矩阵形式

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
2m + M &amp; \frac{3}{2} L m &amp; \frac{1}{2} L m \\
\frac{3}{2} L m &amp; J + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m &amp; \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \\
\frac{1}{2} L m &amp; \frac{1}{2} L^2 m &amp; J + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \\
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{x} \\
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2 \\
\end{bmatrix}
+\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; k_t + \frac{3 g L m}{2} &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{g L m}{2} \\
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
x \\
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2 \\
\end{bmatrix}=
\begin{bmatrix}
F \\
-FL \\
-FL \\
\end{bmatrix}
$$"><p>平衡时有<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="47.552ex" height="2.769ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -1030 21018.1 1224" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" div.data-content:
由 Hamilton 原理

$$\int \delta T + \delta W d t = 0$$

由$\delta W = - \delta V + \delta W_{nc}$

$$\int \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc}d t = 0$$

记坐标原点为$P$

$$
\begin{cases}
PO &= (x, 0) \\
OA &= (L \sin \theta_1,L \cos \theta_1) \\
AB &= (L \sin \theta_2,L \cos \theta_2) \\
PO1&= PO + \frac{1}{2}OA \\
PA &= PO + OA \\
PO2&= PA + \frac{1}{2}AB \\
PB &= PA + AB
\end{cases}
$$

则能量

$$
\begin{cases}
E_M &= \frac{1}{2}M \dot {PO}^2 \\
E_{m_1} &= \frac{1}{2}m \dot {PO_1}^2 + \frac{1}{2}J \dot \theta_1 ^2\\
E_{m_2} &= \frac{1}{2}m \dot {PO_2}^2 + \frac{1}{2}J \dot \theta_2 ^2\\
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
T &= E_M + E_{m_1} + E_{m_2} \\
&=\frac{1}{2} M \dot{x}^2 + \frac{1}{2} m \left( \frac{1}{4} L^2 \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin^2 \theta_1 + \left( \frac{1}{2} L \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \dot{x} \right)^2 \right) + \frac{1}{2} J \dot{\theta}_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} m \left( \left( -L \dot{\theta}_1 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L \dot{\theta}_2 \sin \theta_2 \right)^2 + \left( L \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + \dot{x} \right)^2 \right) + \frac{1}{2} J \dot{\theta}_2^2 \\
&= {\frac{1}{2}J\dot \theta _1^2 + \frac{5}{8}{L^2}m\dot \theta _1^2 + \frac{1}{2}J\dot \theta _2^2 + \frac{1}{8}{L^2}m\dot \theta _2^2 + m{{\dot x}^2} + \frac{1}{2}M{{\dot x}^2} + \frac{3}{2}Lm{{\dot \theta }_1}\dot x\cos {\theta _1} + \frac{1}{2}{L^2}m{{\dot \theta }_1}{{\dot \theta }_2}\cos ({\theta _1} - {\theta _2}) + \frac{1}{2}Lm{{\dot \theta }_2}\dot x\cos {\theta _2}}
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta T &= \frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{x}} \delta \dot{x} + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} \delta \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} \delta \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial x} \delta x + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_1} \delta \theta_1 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_2} \delta \theta_2
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{x}} &= 2 m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} &= J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} &= J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial x} &= 0 \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_1} &= -\frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{x} \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \\
\frac{\partial T}{\partial \theta_2} &= \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \dot{x} \sin \theta_2
\end{cases}
$$

势能

$$
\begin{cases}
E_{k_1} &= \frac{1}{2} k_1 x^2 \\
E_{k_2} &= \frac{1}{2} k_2 x^2 \\
E_{k_T} &= \frac{1}{2} k_T \theta_1^2 \\
E_{g_1} &= m g \left(L-\frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_1\right) \\
E_{g_2} &= m g \left(2L - L \cos \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_2\right) \\
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
V &= E_{k_1} + E_{k_2} + E_{k_T} + E_{g_1} + E_{g_2} \\
&=\frac{1}{2} k_1 x^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 x^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_t \theta_1^2 + mg\left(L - \frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_1\right) + mg\left(2L - L \cos \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta_2\right)
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\frac{\partial V}{\partial x} = k_1 x + k_2 x \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{x}} = 0 \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \theta_1} = k_t \theta_1 + \frac{3 L mg \sin \theta_1}{2} \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} = 0 \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \theta_2} = \frac{L mg \sin \theta_2}{2} \\
\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} = 0
\end{cases}
$$

非保守力做功

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W_{nc} &= -F \delta PB_x \\
&= -F \delta(L \sin \theta_1 + L \sin \theta_2 + x
)\\
&= -F L \cos \theta_1 \delta \theta_1 - F L \cos \theta_2 \delta \theta_2 - F \delta x
\end{align*}
$$

分别考虑三项

考虑$x$

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} \, dt &= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} (\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{x}} \delta \dot{x} + \frac{\partial T}{\partial {x}} \delta {x}) - (\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{x}} \delta \dot{x} + \frac{\partial V}{\partial {x}} \delta {x}) + (- F \delta x) \, dt\\
&= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left [\left( 2m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \dot{x} - (k_1 + k_2)x \delta x - F \delta x \right ]d t \\
&= \left( 2m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta x \bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} \\
&\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \frac{d}{dt} \left( 2m \dot{x} + M \dot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta x \, dt \\
&\quad- \int_{t_1}^{t_2}((k_1 + k_2)x + F) \delta x \, dt \\
&= -\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( 2m \ddot{x} + M \ddot{x} - \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2^2 \sin \theta_2 + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F \right) \delta x \, dt
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\delta x$的任意性, 所以

$$2m \ddot{x} + M \ddot{x} - \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2^2 \sin \theta_2 + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F = 0$$

考虑$\theta_1$

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} \, dt
&= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} (\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} \delta \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial {\theta}_1} \delta {\theta}_1) - (\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_1} \delta \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{\partial V}{\partial {\theta}_1} \delta {\theta}_1) + (- F L \cos \theta_1 \delta \theta_1) \, dt\\
&= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left [\left( J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \dot{\theta}_1 \right. \\
&\quad + \left( -\frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{x} \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \theta_1 \\
&\quad \left. - \left( k_t \theta_1 + \frac{3 L mg \sin \theta_1}{2}\right) \delta \theta_1 - F L \cos \theta_1 \delta \theta_1 \right ]d t \\
&= \left( J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \theta_1 \bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} \\
&\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \frac{d}{dt} \left( J \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \right) \delta \theta_1 \, dt \\
&\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{x} \sin \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + k_t \theta_1 + \frac{3 L mg \sin \theta_1}{2} + F L \cos \theta_1 \right) \delta \theta_1 \, dt \\
&= -\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( F L \cos(\theta_1) + \theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_2^2}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1) \ddot{x}}{2} \right) \delta \theta_1 \, dt
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\delta \theta_1$的任意性, 所以

$$F L \cos(\theta_1) + \theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_2^2}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1) \ddot{x}}{2} =0$$

考虑$\theta_2$

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} \, dt
&= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} (\frac{\partial T}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} \delta \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{\partial T}{\partial {\theta}_2} \delta {\theta}_2) - (\frac{\partial V}{\partial \dot{\theta}_2} \delta \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{\partial V}{\partial {\theta}_2} \delta {\theta}_2) + (- F L \cos \theta_2 \delta \theta_2) \, dt \\
&= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left [\left( J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \dot{\theta}_2 \right. \\
&\quad + \left( \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \dot{x} \sin \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \\
&\quad \left. - \left( \frac{L mg \sin \theta_2}{2} \right) \delta \theta_2 - F L \cos \theta_2 \delta \theta_2 \right ]d t \\
&= \left( J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} \\
&\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \frac{d}{dt} \left( J \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{x} \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \, dt \\
&\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( -\frac{1}{2} L^2 m \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) + \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2 \dot{x} \sin \theta_2 + \frac{L mg \sin \theta_2}{2} + F L \cos \theta_2 \right) \delta \theta_2 \, dt \\
&= F L \cos(\theta_2) + \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} - \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_1^2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \cos(\theta_2) \ddot{x}}{2}
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\delta \theta_2$的任意性, 所以

$$F L \cos(\theta_2) + \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} - \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_1^2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \cos(\theta_2) \ddot{x}}{2} = 0$$

综上, EOM 为

$$
\begin{cases}
2m \ddot{x} + M \ddot{x} - \frac{3}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_1^2 \sin \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} L m \dot{\theta}_2^2 \sin \theta_2 + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \theta_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \theta_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F &= 0 \\
F L \cos(\theta_1) + \theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_2^2}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1) \ddot{x}}{2} &=0 \\
F L \cos(\theta_2) + \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} - \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \dot{\theta}_1^2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2) \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \cos(\theta_2) \ddot{x}}{2} &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

矩阵形式

$$

\frac{3 L m \cos(\theta_1)}{2} & J + \frac{5 L^2 m}{4} & \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2)}{2} \\
\frac{L m \cos(\theta_2)}{2} & \frac{L^2 m \cos(\theta_1 - \theta_2)}{2} & J + \frac{L^2 m}{4}
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix} \ddot{x} \\ \ddot{\theta}_1 \\ \ddot{\theta}_2 \end{bmatrix} +
\begin{bmatrix}
0 & -\frac{3}{2} L m \sin \theta_1 & -\frac{1}{2} L m \sin \theta_2 \\
0 & 0 & \frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2)}{2} \\
0 & -\frac{L^2 m \sin(\theta_1 - \theta_2)}{2} & 0
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix} \dot{x}^2 \\ \dot{\theta}_1^2 \\ \dot{\theta}_2^2 \end{bmatrix} +
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & k_t & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 0
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix} x \\ \theta_1 \\ \theta_2 \end{bmatrix} =
\begin{bmatrix}
-F \\
-F L \cos(\theta_1) - \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} \\
-F L \cos(\theta_2) - \frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2}
\end{bmatrix}
$$

div.data-content:
平衡时有$\dot{x} = 0, \dot{\theta}_1 = 0, \dot{\theta}_2 = 0, \ddot{x} = 0, \ddot{\theta}_1 = 0, \ddot{\theta}_2 = 0, F = 0$

$$
\begin{cases}
(k_1 + k_2)x = 0 \\
\theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \sin(\theta_1)}{2} = 0 \\
\frac{g L m \sin(\theta_2)}{2} = 0
\end{cases}
\Rightarrow
\begin{cases}
x &= 0 \\
\theta_1 &= 0 \\
\theta_2 &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

线性化, 忽略高阶无穷小

$$
\begin{align}
\sin \theta = \theta \\
\cos \theta = 1 \\
y^2 = 0
\end{align}
$$

则有

$$
\begin{cases}
(2m + M) \ddot{x} + \frac{3}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{1}{2} L m \ddot{\theta}_2 + (k_1 + k_2)x + F = 0 \\
\theta_1 k_t + \frac{3 g L m \theta_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{5 L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{4} + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{2} + \frac{3 L m \ddot{x}}{2} + F L = 0 \\
\frac{g L m \theta_2}{2} + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_1}{2} + J \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{L^2 m \ddot{\theta}_2}{4} + \frac{L m \ddot{x}}{2} + F L = 0
\end{cases}
$$

矩阵形式

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
2m + M & \frac{3}{2} L m & \frac{1}{2} L m \\
\frac{3}{2} L m & J + \frac{5}{4} L^2 m & \frac{1}{2} L^2 m \\
\frac{1}{2} L m & \frac{1}{2} L^2 m & J + \frac{1}{4} L^2 m \\
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{x} \\
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2 \\
\end{bmatrix}
+\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & k_t + \frac{3 g L m}{2} & 0 \\
0 & 0 & \frac{g L m}{2} \\
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
x \\
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2 \\
\end{bmatrix}=
\begin{bmatrix}
F \\
-FL \\
-FL \\
\end{bmatrix}
$$
